column5: ~~~~Whats that you say wife gone shoppen   and you are bored,    seen all the phishen shows,   Bass out of season, boat put away for the winter, ice not safe, and the wife has a Honey To Do List    why not drop in at the Rock&Reel in Oshawa. Heard there going to be some hearty Eggnog   being served. Just think a tackle shop and bar, a great place to do some shopping, and have some   Chritmas Cheer also.  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~And no I'm not getting paid to post this
